{"tid":1961683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若果港台撚WHO唔合一國兩制原則，咁\"香港經濟貿易文化辦事處（台灣） \"究竟合唔合一國兩制原則?","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:55:53.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4331b146c35a870e25b77ca70ae24b398bb7d04","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hketco.hk/tc/about_us/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hketco.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fcontact_us.html&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=604d4258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hketco.hk/tc/about_us/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n地址  台灣台北市信義區松高路11號<br />\n統一國際大樓25樓<br />\n香港經濟貿易文化辦事處（台灣）<br />\n（郵遞區號：110060） <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQBnmxc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQBnmxc.png&h=c98ab4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你老母個臭西，你夠唔夠膽寫&quot;香港經濟貿易文化辦事處（中國台灣）&quot;？<br />\n你點解唔將全部台灣一詞都加晒中國o係前面呀?<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華，你記唔記得台灣有班AO?<br />\n<br />\n你寫出黎蔡英文即刻踢晒你班AO落海等佢地游水返香港呀撚屌"},{"pid":"9c28328391ff5aa8db76c05b39de2cd20300deba","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"推到邱騰華同777應機"},{"pid":"87d0f56c3fb3d8c822d328af384b794a95a03801","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"出黎應機啦"},{"pid":"fc1238a956545b97ccb07b27ff7c0301de0c47a7","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"應下啦，加唔加支那去前面好呀"},{"pid":"b12f6c9039446dbe67b4f2617f3776d0380fa849","tid":1961683,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/03/24/phpM3icxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2FphpM3icxD.jpg&h=8f407fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首公然接見由台灣地區非法政權選出嘅高雄地方官員 等同承認台灣擁有獨立主權 間接否定中國於台灣地區嘅合法管治權 特首此舉嚴重踐踏「一中原則」 理應按照《基本法》立即罷免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6654d0baac19b8316e7fa22ab620576e398755e5","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"又推下先"},{"pid":"e406a54d8f42830b09e9780d955a9631f271e112","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"再推下先"},{"pid":"0dcb20d9dc002477a2e96b18bf4d54d304753d06","tid":1961683,"uid":296902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54dc69cdb781d5f0cebc5082cdef9f865d3d6bb4","tid":1961683,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"acd7f914ff52f54c2ec054649b9e4b512cf656da","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"改唔改地址?"},{"pid":"cfe7d23017b30eb365c63be58652c78c6fa02623","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"一中呀，改地址啦！"},{"pid":"a339bbaa2820d5b473b8a5ac613df5a301e9d66e","tid":1961683,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭胸又話上連登嘅"},{"pid":"78bcbeda47de8b91323555980063a91c4a4fea92","tid":1961683,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"一中唔係大過天咩"},{"pid":"64e2685106d30712010472c96b011571f8d32457","tid":1961683,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a2fa2a934a5f888e5e7b93d1e78d13df1c2ef5f","tid":1961683,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2c9e79149c159c3